          <ul>
            <li class="lead" style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14pt"> <strong>Experience reports</strong> should thoroughly describe a computing education intervention and its context. They must present enough details to allow adoption by third parties, in addition to offering an in-depth reflection on what worked (or not) and why. </li>
          </ul>

